elements.name: As a user I can create a new post with 9 characters without spaces

steps.name: I enter "marisela.delvalle93@gmail.com" into input field having className "email"
I enter "12345678" into input field having className "password"
I click on element having className "login"
I click on element that links to "#/posts/"
I click on element that links to "#/editor/post/"
I enter "AabbccddF" into input field having className "gh-editor-title"
I enter "Description" into input field having className "koenig-editor__editor"
I click on element having className "gh-publishmenu"
I click on element having className "gh-publishmenu-button"
